<!:TITLE=Handing over Units><l:helppage><l:helphead>Handing over Units to Allies<l:/helphead>
<l:helpbody>
It is possible to hand over units to your allied players. Therefore, when planning your stategies you should think of this possibility, since your goal is not just to be the only ruler in the world but to win the game by letting you and your allied players beat the enemy as one.

You hand over the units by simply moving them into the allied players areas.





<l:/helpbody><l:/helppage>
